						<div class="postbody">To improve it even better, each scanline would have been 341.25 pixels (1365 master clocks) long, with the extra master clock not inserted during each of the three lines of vsync. But that would probably have required more logic (therefore more expensive die area and/or more circuit golf) than what they ended up doing.</div>

